Class JsonCreator

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.JsonCreator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ChangesMatchObserver, ChangesObserver, CreationGameObserver, LobbyListener
    public class JsonCreator
extends java.lang.Object
implements ChangesObserver, CreationGameObserver, LobbyListener, ChangesMatchObserver
    Represent an object that is an observer of the whole model and when notified remembers the changes. Then is able to create a json file with all the information regarding the model
